つくることが政治の責任、これこそ…", "…れこそが経済の好循環を生み出す。だから、私たちはその仕組みとして、内部留保の一部に課税をして、それでさっき言った中小企業の賃上げの直接助成に…", "…さん、私たち、是非自民党の皆さんとも議論したいんですよ。総理、この内部留保に課税をすることで賃上げの原資にしていく、中小企業を直接支援して。…"]}, {"url": "https://kokkai.ndl.go.jp/txt/121215261X00520231128/345", "sentence": []}, {"url": "https://kokkai.ndl.go.jp/txt/121215261X00520231128/347", "sentence": []}, {"url": "https://kokkai.ndl.go.jp/txt/121215261X00520231128/349", "sentence": []}, {"url": "https://kokkai.ndl.go.jp/txt/121215261X00520231128/352", "sentence": []}, {"url": "https://kokkai.ndl.go.jp/txt/121215261X00520231128/354", "sentence": []}, {"url": "https://kokkai.ndl.go.jp/txt/121215261X00520231128/356", "sentence": []}, {"url": "https://kokkai.ndl.go.jp/txt/121215261X00520231128/358", "sentence": []}, {"url": "https://kokkai.ndl.go.jp/txt/121215261X00520231128/360", "sentence": []}, {"url": "https://kokkai.ndl.go.jp/txt/121215261X00520231128/363", "sentence": []}, {"url": "https://kokkai.ndl.go.jp/txt/121215261X00520231128/365", "sentence": []}, {"url": "https://kokkai.ndl.go.jp/txt/121215261X00520231128/367", "sentence": []}, {"url": "https://kokkai.ndl.go.jp/txt/121215261X00520231128/369", "sentence": []}, {"url": "https://kokkai.ndl.go.jp/txt/121215261X00520231128/371", "sentence": []}, {"url": "https://kokkai.ndl.go.jp/txt/121215261X00520231128/373", "sentence": []}, {"url": "https://kokkai.ndl.go.jp/txt/121215261X00520231128/375", "sentence": []}, {"url": "https://kokkai.ndl.go.jp/txt/121215261X00520231128/377", "sentence": []}, {"url": "https://kokkai.ndl.go.jp/txt/121215261X00520231128/379", "sentence": []}, {"url": "https://kokkai.ndl.go.jp/txt/121215261X00520231128/381", "sentence": []}, {"url": "https://kokkai.ndl.go.jp/txt/121215261X00520231128/383", "sentence": []}, {"url": "https://kokkai.ndl.go.jp/txt/121215261X00520231128/385", "sentence": []}]}]}, {"date": "2024-02-02", "meeting": [{"meeting_name": "参議院 本会議", "remarks": [{"url": "https://kokkai.ndl.go.jp/txt/121315254X00420240202/13", "sentence": ["…らないのか、そ